longBusinessSummary: Auren Energia S.A. engages in the planning, construction, installation, operation, and maintenance of renewable energy generation assets in Brazil. It operates wind, solar, and hydroelectric energy generation systems with a total installed capacity of 3,030 MW. The company was formerly known as VTRM Energia Participações S.A. and changed its name to Auren Energia S.A. in March 2022. Auren Energia S.A. is headquartered in São Paulo, Brazil.
